    "Background": {
      "text": "Lymphadenitis = inflammation of lymph node\nCan be single or multiple\nMost commonly due to\nviral\nor\nbacterial disease\n(usually\nstaph\nor\nstrep\n) infection local to region draining lymph to that node\nPyogenic organisms may cause suppurative infection/abscess\nNot to be confused with\nlymphangitis",
